How & where to start giving others

[/vc_column_text][distance type="5"][distance type="5"][distance type="5"][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section][vc_row row_dark="yes" wn_bg_color="#282828" css=".vc_custom_1483344317752{margin-top: -120px !important;}"][vc_column][distance type="5"][title_p_text align="center" top_title="Let's find out" top_title_part_1="Why we believe" top_title_part_2="Giving matters"][distance type="5"][vc_row_inner layer_animation="true"][vc_column_inner width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1483344289126{border-right-width: 1px !important;padding-right: 5% !important;padding-left: 10% !important;border-right-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.11) !important;border-right-style: solid !important;}"][vc_column_text]
TAKING THE STEP OF FAITH

When you participate in online giving, you decide in advance to faithfully give. God always blesses that kind of faith!

 
SIMPLIFYING YOUR LIFE

Online giving is simple, easy, and also reduces post office trips, postage costs and weekly/monthly check-writing chores.

 
HELPING THE CHURCH TO SERVE OTHERS

administrative overhead costs thus, putting more of your dollars to work in the ministries.

item.content:encoded:
[vc_section align_center="aligncenter" white_text_color="yes" wn_parallax="content-moving" wn_parallax_speed="190" css=".vc_custom_1485762761308{background-image: url(http://webnus.co/dummy/vision/forward/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/blx17.jpg?id=9976) !important;}"][vc_row layer_animation="true"][vc_column][distance type="5"][distance type="5"][distance type="2"][distance type="5"][vc_column_text enable_animation_pro="true" trigger_hook="0.1" duration="900" vertical_movement="100" opacity="0"]

Women Ministry

[/vc_column_text][distance type="5"][distance type="5"][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section][vc_section][vc_row layer_animation="true"][vc_column width="1/3"][distance type="5"][vc_column_text el_class="brdr-r1" css=".vc_custom_1483784285162{margin-right: 30px !important;padding-right: 30px !important;}"]

01. EXPLORE

Connecting Women

In ur church we belive that women ministry exists to connect you to God and also ministry is amazing community for people who want help.

[/vc_column_text][distance type="5"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3"][distance type="5"][vc_column_text el_class="brdr-r1" css=".vc_custom_1483784277849{margin-right: 30px !important;padding-right: 30px !important;}"]

02. EMPOWER

Equpping Women

Our women ministry exists to provide you with tools and resources to help you ignite your passions, deepen your faith in Jesus, and lead a purpose-driven life.

[/vc_column_text][distance type="5"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3"][distance type="5"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483784269577{margin-right: 30px !important;padding-right: 30px !important;}"]

03. ENGAGE

Igniting Women

We believe our community gives you opportunities to express your shape for ministry and live your life on mission, empowering you to live boldly.

[/vc_column_text][distance type="5"][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section][vc_section css=".vc_custom_1483783237471{background-color: #f7f7f7 !important;}"][vc_row layer_animation="true"][vc_column][distance type="5"][distance type="5"][title_p_text align="center" top_title="Discover the church" top_title_part_1="An Overview About" top_title_part_2="Church Ministry"][distance type="5"][distance][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row content_placement="middle" layer_animation="true"][vc_column width="1/12"][/vc_column][vc_column width="4/12"][ourteam type="4" img="10951" name="Victoria Milner" title="Women Minstry" social="enable" first_url="#" second_url="#"][/vc_column][vc_column width="6/12"][vc_column_text]What is Women ministry about? Womens Ministry exists to lead women in a growing relationship with Jesus Christ. We are friends: old friends making new friends, always allowing the circle to grow wider. We are sisters: accepting one another and challenging each other to grow in our faith. We are image-bearers: like Father, like daughter, we take Christ in us to our community, revealing His love and grace to a broken world. We hope youll join us as we grow in our relationship with Jesus together. If you have questions, please feel free to contact me. Let us think of ways to motivate one another to acts of love and good works. And let us not neglect our meeting together.   What do we care about? Experience heartfelt worship, good friends and a refreshing look into Gods Word in a comfortable, casual setting. Spring, Summer, and Fall semesters offered. LEADER PASTOR
[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][distance type="2"][vc_column_text]

Life Story

My wife, Amanda, and I married in 1980. Our daughter Sarah was born in USA in 2000 our son, David, was born in Fort Worth in 2005; and our daughter Lynda was born in Grapevine in 2006. What do you like to do in your free time? In my free time, I plan what Im going to do the next time I have free time. Actually, I realize Ill never get these days back with my kids, so my free time is mostly with Lynda and them. I enjoy running, cycling, watching movies and sports, cleaning my garage, and doing nothing. Job Description? We are seeking a full-time Children's Pastor to minister to children from birth through fifth grade. This individual will be responsible for recruitment, training and development of volunteer leaders in a church of 600. Primary objectives are to evangelize and disciple children and resource parents and families. Individual will implement and oversee the development of Orange Philosophy and oversee all aspects of programming on Mondays and Tuesdays. Successful candidates should demonstrate proven leadership abilities, be an effective communicator, energetic, highly creative, and able to plan and implement programs in a team-oriented environment. College degree and experience leading a vibrant children's ministry is preferred. Des Moines First Assembly is one church with two locations.[/vc_column_text][distance type="2"][/vc_column][/vc_row]

And beneath the effulgent Antarctic skies I have boarded the Argo-Navis, and joined the chase against the starry Cetus far beyond the utmost stretch of Hydrus and the Flying Fish. five long years, he wore this watch up his ass. then, when he died of dysentery, he gave me the watch. i'm neglecting my other guests. enjoy yourself, you'll find the young ladies stimulating company.

Fasces of harpoons for spurs

With a frigate's anchors for my bridle-bitts and fasces of harpoons for spurs, would I could mount that whale and leap the topmost skies, to see whether the fabled heavens with all their countless tents really lie encamped beyond!

Then they show that show to the people
